18/12/2017 - v1.2.0

- the web UI supports multiple targets and sources,
- added monitoring probe for th web UI, nagios compatible,
- various bug fixes,
- added management scripts to keep synchronized the various tables of th back-end DB.

10/10/2016 - v1.1.0 beta

- the web UI offers the possibility 
  * to link together two policies via policy id,
  * to address a collection using an iRODS path or a PID.
- the back-end DB is now an XML DB, implemented through BASEX.
- the agent is now able 
  * to generate test rules for the downloaded policies
  * to list the available policies in the DB filtering the list
  * to update the status of the policy on the DB
